We had lost the most genious mind in the world. I am brazilian and I have been following the trajectory of Jobs since Apple started the biggest technology researches in cellphone and informatics in this decade. A persuasive man,
 full of knowledge and faith in his words and job. Let God now take care of you. Rest in peace Steve Jobs and thank you about all those things that make people life's easier.
